# .cursorrules - Research_Map Project

This repository follows the **Research_Map** framework.

## Where to Read Rules

- `.cursor/rules/global.mdc`
- `AGENTS.md`
- `docs/_INDEX.md`
- `docs/workflows/RESEARCH_MANAGEMENT.md`
- `plans/_INDEX.md`

## Quick Constraints

1. `docs/` is the system of record.
2. `guide/` is read-only.
3. Update `<!-- reviewed: YYYY-MM-DD -->` for doc edits.
4. Never invent citations; verify or mark placeholders.
5. Run `scripts/check-structure.sh`, `scripts/check-doc-freshness.sh`, `scripts/check-agent-files.sh`, `scripts/check-doc-links.sh`, `scripts/check-doc-index-coverage.sh`, and `scripts/check-plan-index.sh`.
